The paper deals with image captioning, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The dataset is specifically designed to address the interests of people who are blind, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses the challenges faced by modern image captioning algorithms, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG).
